        <p>
            <h3>1 - Visa extension</h3>
            Visa extension is applied for foreigners wanting to prolong their current stay in Vietnam without leaving the country. The Immigration department is to grant an extension stamp for 1month or 3months.<br />
            <i>Note:</i>Visa extension is good for a single entry only and visa-holders must stay in Vietnam for under a year.
        </p>
